title: Miss Fortune - Just another game in Low Elo

embed.description: I've been playing some Miss Fortune to get into Silver. One particular game stood out to me, it had some very interesting moments ;) This was in Patch 7.4, before MF's nerf in 7.5 and changes in 7.6. Enjoy!

body:
Hi everyone,

I've been playing some Miss Fortune to get into Silver. One particular game stood out to me, it had some very interesting moments
This video highlights highlights those moments + the usual low elo mistakes ;).

Thanks, and enjoy!
